    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Backrooms: Found Footage</strong> is a single-player horror game where you are the main character trying to survive the Backrooms. Curiosity wins and you decide to explore this weird place that you got trapped in. What could go wrong?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a <u>Found-Footage</u> style horror game where your main objective is to find the way out of the <strong>Backrooms</strong>. You play as <strong>Young Alex</strong> who got trapped in the <strong>Backrooms</strong>, not knowing anything about it. You decide to record this little adventure, but you manage to capture something really weird.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215190/extras/d85bf698a6b74de1cc7dbc57a3ae7353.avif?t=1762523185\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not recommended for lower-end systems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*Inspired by Kane Pixels</strong></p>",
